* Appendix: Contributors to [[Cosmic Background Explorer|COBE]] * To Dig Deeper: Further Readings * Acknowledgments * Index
== In popular culture == ''Wrinkles in Time'' was featured in an episode of ''[[The Big Bang Theory|Big Bang Theory]]''. In the episode "[[The Terminator Decoupling]]", [[Leonard Hofstadter]] was reading a copy of the book on the train. At the end of the episode, author George Smoot made a cameo appearance.
